{"tid":1762105,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"法 國 工 會 發 起 下 周 四 全 國 大 罷 工","createTime":"2019-11-29T10:54:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T16:32:15.000Z","uid":22675,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e2bfba560ea956a250ea96a1768e3d98a1a1ccf4","tid":1762105,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T10:54:18.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】法國多個工會發起下周四全國大罷工，癱瘓陸空交通，企圖迫使政府放棄改革退休金制度，有工會揚言會持續罷工，直至當局回應訴求。<br />\n<br />\n法國反對政府推行各種民生政策的示威不絕，繼日前有上千名來自全國各地的農民駕駛拖拉機到巴黎阻塞交通，抗議馬克龍政府禁用除草劑草甘膦等政策，影響他們的生計，多個大型工會更發動下周四全國大罷工，再次要求當局擱置備受爭議的退休金改革計劃。<br />\n<br />\n預料鐵路工人、地鐵和巴士車長、航空公司地勤人員、航空交通管制員、運輸業工人、郵差和教師等都會參與，陸空交通勢將大受影響。<br />\n<br />\n現時法國有多達42種不同的退休金計算方法，政府提出設立全民統一的退休金計分制度，確保各行各業的人享有同等權益。在新制度下，原本每月退休金相對豐厚的公共交通業員工獲得的金額會大幅減少，工會也擔心曾失業一段時間或起薪點低的工人會受剝削。<br />\n<br />\n當地數個大型工會均表示，由於政府一直漠視反對聲音，他們迫不得已發起罷工，又強調退休金改革不止損害鐵路工人權益，對全國都有負面影響，有工會更警告，罷工可能會持續一段長時間，直至政府回應訴求。<br />\n<br />\n前年上任時，承諾全面改革社會保障制度的總統馬克龍批評，罷工人士的訴求會損害全社會的利益。<br />\n<br />\n有官員則形容罷工匪夷所思，因為退休金制度改革的諮詢工作仍在進行中，政府會繼續與工會對話。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐法國大使館提醒在法國或計劃到法國的中國公民，在大罷工期間注意安全和謹慎安排出行計劃，避免發生意外。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=371659\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D371659&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY17Oh%2FyAFRgp1rU3tL1w%2BGY%3D&h=93f2aee5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D371659&h=3c64bccf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=371659</a>"},{"pid":"0bfcc7fe0ae08f0eb1d85f453bf38bce6888016c","tid":1762105,"uid":21141,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T10:56:21.000Z","msg":"有工會真係屈機好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c80730dcc6baa5a174f0e0357bce3dd538126189","tid":1762105,"uid":44298,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T10:57:36.000Z","msg":"法國有咩都會全世界罷工，好正"},{"pid":"e00bd77bac014844cca37d4b4005706537db66c1","tid":1762105,"uid":12526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T11:03:10.000Z","msg":"法國人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32aa75cd3e46321b482034ae02ca55dacbc54977","tid":1762105,"uid":30084,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0bfcc7fe0ae08f0eb1d85f453bf38bce6888016c","tid":1762105,"uid":21141,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T10:56:21.000Z","msg":"有工會真係屈機好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T11:05:39.000Z","msg":"係鬼佬高質 唔係公會問題<br />\n<br />\n國泰公會領袖有版你睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n炒左 就冇野"},{"pid":"d3932058b49f0568f4397637a9965732c0b41e4e","tid":1762105,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T11:06:47.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc1e7657de8cee0ff1b36eac7612454575c524be","tid":1762105,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T11:07:03.000Z","msg":"我地可唔可以派代表團去參考法式工會"},{"pid":"b2de84b82684e477961fe097efff425896af3075","tid":1762105,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T11:07:25.000Z","msg":"法國佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"923a45ebcc0bec21eb19af2a7d8253632bc2f3b7","tid":1762105,"uid":209333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T11:07:56.000Z","msg":"革命大國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4205c09c6485b5df57a646a5324762578a1c644","tid":1762105,"uid":21920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T11:08:48.000Z","msg":"可以參考"},{"pid":"05ad3997a78124ed